---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ancillary Services – Bliss Dermacare" description="IV Hydration Therapy, Personalized Lab Collection, Hormone Lab Panel Support, and Regenerative Blood-Based Services at Bliss Dermacare in Tampa, FL.">

  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">All Services</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Ancillary Services</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Total Body Wellness</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Ancillary Services</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Complementary wellness services that go beyond aesthetics — supporting your health, performance, and longevity from the inside out.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <!-- IV Hydration Therapy -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/iv-hydration-therapy.jpg" alt="IV Hydration Therapy — intravenous vitamin and mineral drip treatment" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">IV Hydration Therapy</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Replenish vitamins, minerals, and fluids directly into the bloodstream for immediate absorption. Customized IV drip formulas for energy, immunity, recovery, skin glow, or hydration.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>100% direct IV absorption</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Custom formula for your goals</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Energy, immunity, recovery &amp; glow options</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Results felt within hours</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$149</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 min / session</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="iv-hydration-therapy" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Personalized Lab Collection -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/lab-collection-bloodwork.jpg" alt="Personalized lab collection — blood draw for total body optimization" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Personalized Lab Collection</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Comprehensive bloodwork drawn and analyzed for total body optimization. Know exactly where you stand with key biomarkers for health, performance, and longevity.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Complete metabolic &amp; CBC panels</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Thyroid, vitamin D, iron &amp; more</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Results reviewed with provider</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Optimized for your health goals</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$199</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">30 min / draw</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="lab-collection" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Hormone Lab Panel Support -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/hormone-lab-panel.jpg" alt="Hormone lab panel — medical consultation and blood test support" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Hormone Lab Panel Support</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">A specialized hormone panel draw with clinical consultation to evaluate testosterone, estrogen, cortisol, thyroid, and other key hormones affecting energy, mood, body composition, and vitality.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Testosterone, estrogen &amp; cortisol</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Thyroid (TSH, T3, T4) included</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Clinical consultation with results</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Personalized optimization plan</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$349</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">45 min / session</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="hormone-lab-panel" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Regenerative Blood-Based Services -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6823564/pexels-photo-6823564.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Regenerative blood-based services exosomes and plasma therapy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Regenerative Blood-Based Services</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Advanced regenerative therapies using your body's own biological components — including PRP derivatives, exosomes, and plasma-based protocols — to accelerate healing, repair, and rejuvenation.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Exosome &amp; PRP-derived therapies</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Plasma-based healing protocols</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Accelerated tissue repair</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Consultation required</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$450</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 min / session</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="regenerative-blood-services" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Also Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/services/advanced-treatments/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Advanced Treatments</a>
        <a href="/services/facials/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Facials</a>
        <a href="/services/semipermanent-makeup/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Semipermanent Makeup</a>
        <a href="/services/lash-brow-body/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Lash, Brow &amp; Body</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to book?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">All ancillary services are standalone bookings. We'll confirm your appointment within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-lg">Request Booking <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
